        "\n\n ∫cosec x dx = ∫dx/(sin x) = ∫dx/(2 sin x/2  cos x/2) \n = ∫ 1/2 sec²  x/2 dx/ tan  x/2	 [Multiply the lobe and denominator by sec²  x/2] \n = ∫ dz/z/z ;  [If tan x/2 = z then 1/2 sec² x/2 dx = dz] \n = ln | z |  = ln | tan x/2 |  = ln tan x/2",
