      question: "অনির্দিষ্ট যোগজ নির্ণয়ের সূত্রঃ ∫cosec x dx = ?",
      attribute: "",
      op1: "∫cosec x dx = - ln tan x",
      op2: "∫cosec x dx = - ln tan x/2",
      op3: "∫cosec x dx = - ln sin x/2",
      op4: "∫cosec x dx = ln tan x/2	",
      proof:
        "\n\n ∫cosec x dx = ∫dx/(sin x) = ∫dx/(2 sin x/2  cos x/2) \n = ∫ 1/2 sec²  x/2 dx/ tan  x/2	 [লব ও হরকে sec² x/2 দ্বারা গুণ করে] \n = ∫ dz/z/z ;  [If tan x/2 = z then 1/2 sec² x/2 dx = dz] \n = ln | z |  = ln | tan x/2 |  = ln tan x/2",
      pic: "",
