        "\n\n ∫sec x dx = ∫dx/cos⁡x  = ∫dx/(sin (π/2  + x)) \n = ∫dx/(2 sin (π/4  + x/2) cos (π/4  + x/2)) \n = ∫(1/2  sec² (π/4  + x/2) dx)/(tan (π/4  + x/2)) \n ধরি, z = tan (π/4 + x/2 ) = dz = 1/2 sec² (π/4 + x/2) dx \n ∴ ∫sec x dx = ∫dz/z = ln | z | = ln | tan (π/4 + x/2) \n ∴ ∫sec x dx = ln tan(π/4 + x/2)",
